{"tid":1760142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世] 停止送頭，整個社會一同孤立黑警","createTime":"2019-11-28T04:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T17:09:10.000Z","uid":120847,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"edcec3b279953313bf878fdc10f5214c0c3dfc95","tid":1760142,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:19:16.000Z","msg":"區選嘅勝利已經令大家對黑警嘅仇恨淡化<br />\n大家係咪已經原諒左黑警?<br />\n<br />\n721完全無視市民性命安危<br />\n平日以殘害無辜市民為樂，暴力成癮<br />\n完全泯滅人性<br />\n甚至試圖奪權建立軍政府<br />\n呢個與民為敵嘅武裝組織，任何一個有血性嘅人都唔可以忘記佢地嘅所作所為<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地一定要讓仇恨延續下去，<br />\n直至佢地被清算，被唾棄，被毀滅。</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地要令每一個警員都被社會摒棄同孤立<br />\n作為社會一員，你有責任<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1.做生意/開舖嘅你，今日起因行政理由，拒絕服務警員<br />\n<br />\n2. 有朋友親戚做黑警嘅話，同佢立即斷絕來往，並鼓勵其他朋友一同孤立黑警<br />\n<br />\n3. 一同向各國政府要求制裁香港警察<br />\n<br />\n既然大家武力不對等，我地就無謂再送頭<br />\n我地以社會壓力將呢群禽獸孤立起黎<br />\n呢個係作為一個人應有嘅基本良知同底線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5NrSSWn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5NrSSWn.png&h=e8610c37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6voZAe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6voZAe.jpg&h=6ee10906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLasGOA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLasGOA.png&h=d0d7bf15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEAgz8B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEAgz8B.jpg&h=878bcd50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CHUk1OZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCHUk1OZ.jpg&h=1a39d28a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CWxe6fF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCWxe6fF.jpg&h=ba3c5b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RyxiYiQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRyxiYiQ.jpg&h=8b28fb16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E5oJ9qu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE5oJ9qu.jpg&h=735d20fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qP4huqw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqP4huqw.png&h=fadca241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w20P4YS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw20P4YS.jpg&h=b5ee3f53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0tMvPqU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0tMvPqU.png&h=02e96cb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c35d2ed3d2aa11ba826e42c72ae6c51181e8536","tid":1760142,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a301d4d198f7ee714a801198338ca8eb1d3719e0","tid":1760142,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:20:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2945bb20dbd1c5cfccb6c29ae3aa4c32293bf72b","tid":1760142,"uid":303895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:21:10.000Z","msg":"絕對同意 幫推"},{"pid":"be2f229c8b88ec35f5c19628bd2b5a026dc5346f","tid":1760142,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum